<template>
  <v-card
  elevation="2">
    <v-card-title>
        Danh sách phát triển mới fiber
    </v-card-title>
    <v-card-text>
        <v-data-table
            :headers="newHeaders"
            :items="newDesserts"
            :items-per-page="50"
            class="elevation-1"
            height="300px"
        ></v-data-table>
    </v-card-text>
  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
import Factory from '@/server/factory/factory';
import common from '@/server/common/common';
const New = Factory.get('new');
export default {
    data() {
        return {

            //Table New
            newHeaders:[],
            newDesserts:[],

             //userlogin
            ma_ND: null,
            ten_NV: null,
            token: null,
        }
    },
    created () {
        var self=this;
        //Get Info User Login
        var UserLogin = common.GetInfoUserLogin('token_session');
        if(!UserLogin)
            self.$router.push('/login');
        else
        {
            self.ten_NV=UserLogin.ten_NV;
            self.ma_ND=UserLogin.ma_ND;
            self.token=UserLogin.token;
        
        };

        //Get list New

        self.Get_List_New();
    },
    methods: {
        Get_List_New() {
            var self=this;
            New.Get_List_New('',self.token).then(response =>{
                if(response.data.success && response.data.data.length){
                    self.newHeaders=[
                        { text: 'ma_tb', value: 'ma_tb'},
                        { text: 'tb_cd_dongquang', value: 'tb_cd_dongquang'},
                        { text: 'huy_truoc_30ngay', value: 'huy_truoc_30ngay'},
                        { text: 'khongthuoc_khuvuc_pttb', value: 'khongthuoc_khuvuc_pttb'},
                        { text: 'thang_hoamang', value: 'thang_hoamang'},
                        { text: 'ngay_hoamang', value: 'ngay_hoamang'},
                        { text: 'ngay_ins', value: 'ngay_ins'},
                        { text: 'trangthai', value: 'trangthai'},
                        { text: 'goi_tratruoc', value: 'goi_tratruoc'},
                        { text: 'tocdo_id', value: 'tocdo_id'},
                        { text: 'ma_NVKT_TT', value: 'ma_NVKT_TT'},
                        { text: 'hdtb_id', value: 'hdtb_id'},
                        { text: 'hdkh_id', value: 'hdkh_id'},
                        { text: 'thuebao_id', value: 'thuebao_id'},
                        { text: 'kieuld_id', value: 'kieuld_id'},
                        { text: 'phongbh', value: 'phongbh'},
                        { text: 'phongbh_id', value: 'phongbh_id'},
                        { text: 'diachi_ld', value: 'diachi_ld'},
                        { text: 'ngay_tt', value: 'ngay_tt'},
                        { text: 'tb_dungthu', value: 'tb_dungthu'},
                        { text: 'ngay_tao', value: 'ngay_tao'},
  
                        ];
                    self.newDesserts=response.data.data;
                }

            });
            
        }
    },
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
